arraylist is one of the most commonly used data structure in java
it is called as dynamic array 
it is like a regular array but it can grow or shrink in size automatically as you add or remove items

why to arraylist
well in standard java array you must specify the size at the beginning and it can not be changed later
arraylist solves this for you with
flexible size
can only hold objects
but it is slightly slower but more flexible

arraylist cannot store primitive types like int, boolean or char directly 
you must use their wrapper classes
